Package: bootmakr
Title: Bootstrap Inference for Sensemakr Sensitivity Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Wraps sensemakr sensitivity analysis in a bootstrap loop to produce
    bootstrap standard errors, percentile confidence intervals, and p-values for
    adjusted treatment effect estimates. Supports multiple kd values, cluster
    bootstrap, stratified bootstrap, convergence diagnostics, and visualization.
